          About the project
        %p
          Evercheck offers license verification services. They help companies stay ahead with  their industry leading platform. We enhanced the way people interact with their service as a whole. From the first time people view the marketing site, to the interaction design of the native and desktop experience. 
      .col-md-6.col-sm-6
