            Reusable Components
          %p
            After exploring navigation, we identified components of the interface and applied the same extendable thinking. We designed a robust table that allowed for optional functionality based on requirements. We built a color coordinated system for different license types. Also, a way to organize status indications and form elements. All of these elements were key to the functionality of any page.  
